<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="12" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="13.[192,1440,887,1010]" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">
In all trees, 
<taxonomicName authority="R. Felder, 1869" authorityName="R. Felder" authorityYear="1869" box="[378,743,887,911]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Helias" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pallida">
<emphasis box="[378,551,887,911]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">Helias pallida</emphasis>
R. Felder, 1869
</taxonomicName>
is not monophyletic with 
<taxonomicName authority="Cramer, [1779]" authorityName="Cramer" authorityYear="1779" box="[1056,1435,887,911]" class="Insecta" family="Papilionidae" genus="Papilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="busirus">
<emphasis box="[1056,1241,887,911]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">Papilio busirus</emphasis>
Cramer, [1779]
</taxonomicName>
, the 
<typeStatus box="[239,292,921,945]" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">type</typeStatus>
species of 
<taxonomicName authority="Hubner, [1819]" authorityName="Hubner" authorityYear="1819" box="[421,737,920,944]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Achlyodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[421,543,920,944]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">Achlyodes</emphasis>
Hübner, [1819]
</taxonomicName>
, but originates within 
<taxonomicName authority="Boisduval, [1836]" authorityName="Boisduval" authorityYear="1836" box="[1014,1314,920,944]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Eantis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1014,1094,921,944]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">Eantis</emphasis>
Boisduval, [1836]
</taxonomicName>
(
<typeStatus box="[1330,1384,920,944]" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">type</typeStatus>
species 
<taxonomicName authority="Hubner, [1807]" authorityName="Hubner" authorityYear="1807" box="[244,625,953,977]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Urbanus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="thraso">
<emphasis box="[244,435,953,977]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">Urbanus thraso</emphasis>
Hübner, [1807]
</taxonomicName>
) (
<figureCitation box="[649,719,953,977]" captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="14.[192,275,1196,1218]" captionTargetBox="[193,1440,213,1161]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[192,1440,213,1162]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="Figure 5. Genomic trees of Achlyodini. See Fig. 2 legend for notations." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677245" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3677245/files/figure.png" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">Fig. 5</figureCitation>
). Therefore, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="R. Felder" authorityYear="1869" box="[872,996,953,977]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Helias" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pallida">
<emphasis box="[872,996,953,977]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">H. pallida</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is placed in this genus to form a new combination: 
<taxonomicName authority="Boisduval, 1836" authorityName="Cong &amp; Zhang &amp; Shen &amp; Grishin" authorityYear="2019" baseAuthorityName="R. Felder" box="[357,533,986,1010]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Eantis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pallida">
<emphasis box="[357,533,986,1010]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">Eantis pallida</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
